snippet.title: SEGA Master System Brawl - Walkthrough
snippet.description:
SEGA Master System Brawl is a homebrew SEGA Genesis/Mega Drive title that pits 16 iconic Master System characters against each other in a one-one-one fight to determine who reigns supreme.

The game is developed by Bonaf and can currently be downloaded here: http://david.bonafonte.free.fr/SMSBrawl/SMSBrawl.bin
